Rating: 3
This is a keeper. Like another reviewer I combined fresh porcini with the cremini mushrooms. Also used half and half, thickening it with a little Wondra. Eliminated the butter. Finally, used porcini broth (bouillon cubes available at some Italian groceries) which upped the mushroom flavor.

